Database:
- support subtables without rebuilding them for each request.
:: sendao.libsendao = new app.base.rcs.Base('sendao');
   sendao.libsendao = app.base.rcs.getBase('sendao');
or sendao.libsendao = app.base('revision', 'base', {'sendao'}); // db, table, params

Controllers:
- support permissions inside of authentication handler.
:: authSession(params, require_permission_flags)


Tools:
